{"tid":1099120,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)最爆伴郎團1-2 \t搏擊會","createTime":"2019-04-09T14:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T19:11:16.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"367ac6e0558ab62b3343786880b36862870fd4f7","tid":1099120,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:30:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=7c54f0d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=ea6bbd48\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=8750a6d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a>&lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9e/The_Hangover_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9e%2FThe_Hangover_poster.jpg&h=220b9186&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fc/Fight_Club_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffc%2FFight_Club_poster.jpg&h=f3863426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.道格（Doug，賈斯汀&middot;巴薩飾）結婚前，與三個伴郎朋友菲爾（Phil，布萊德利&middot;古柏飾）、史都（Stu，艾德&middot;赫姆斯飾）和艾倫（Alan，查克&middot;葛里芬納奇飾）開車到拉斯維加斯舉辦單身派對。但三位伴郎隔天宿醉醒來，卻發現新郎不見了，而毫無頭緒的三人，得想辦法回想起誘惑&middot;夜發生何事，且把道格找出帶回洛杉磯進行婚禮..<br />\n<br />\n2.位主角在泰國團聚，準備參加史都的婚禮，然而他們又在單身派對的隔天早上於一家破舊的旅館中醒來，完全不知道他們為何身在此處<br />\n<br />\n3.主角（愛德華&middot;諾頓飾）（書中及電影中均沒有提到過主角的名字，IMDb上稱主角為旁白，部分影迷稱其為傑克）為某汽車公司的調查員，因為日復一日無聊的生活使其希望找到各種舒解壓力的出口。郵購各式各樣的高級家具仍無法滿足其日漸枯竭的心靈而導致失眠。於是他找上了自助團體，在那邊他遇見比他過得更悲慘的人們（癌症患者、心理疾病患者等。）藉此催眠自己仍然是過得幸福快樂的；直到瑪拉這個冒牌貨闖進了生命，原本可以讓人放鬆的去處又變成焦慮的來源<br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=9985bddd\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=se%2BVxgw3JrdCjNobn1OhIgp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=2fbcc760\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbe6b2ea14dc421cdf2148533fffb27446726ac","tid":1099120,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73ab0dbe63c99c5d81efdfdfa33d020614225e1","tid":1099120,"uid":29160,"like":0